{
  "stem": "523.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, at that time, now I don't know how it's now, but at that time, they were afraid if the enemy throws some poisonous gases.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he became an instructor.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he was working in another city.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Outside Chernivitsi, that's right.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Only a few days.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then he went to Chernivtsi, maybe to pick up a few of our belongings.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But then if he didn't pick up any things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I've stayed in Edinitsi with this gentleman, [? so-called, ?] supposed to be our friend.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he treated us-- because we survived.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he treated me like-- it was-- I was like a maid, scrubbing floor, doing all manual jobs, in order to have a place where to live, a place where to stay.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was all alone.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Our home was the KGB.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was nationalized.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Everyone was afraid to look at [? them ?] because after all, my father was a rich man.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I am-- and the Russian, I mean, I am a child of a, of a rich man.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "This was a crime.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So-- and I was staying with this gentleman and also another couple.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because most of the Jewish homes were destroyed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So happened they-- the local people thought that the, the Jews buried their gold in the homes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So destroying the homes, looking for gold.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So the few houses that were still left, people of few families or whatever people were living together.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So I was living with this gentleman-- I had my room-- and another couple which she lost her daughter in Transnistria.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This lady before the war was a little bit on her head.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And losing her beautiful daughter didn't help.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she started to hate me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Why her, her daughter [INAUDIBLE] is dead?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And why I am alive?",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
